00:00:09.076 --> 00:00:11.679 position:19% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT] Is this power
she's taking from my heart?

00:00:12.446 --> 00:00:14.649 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA]
I'm seeing a cold winter night

00:00:14.782 --> 00:00:15.984 position:24% line:89% align:start
we spent together.

00:00:16.450 --> 00:00:18.987 position:13% line:89% align:start
Pesha's tiny hand in mine.

00:00:19.654 --> 00:00:22.924 position:7% line:83% align:start
The candle that wouldn't light
on a shivering evening,

00:00:23.257 --> 00:00:26.059 position:24% line:83% align:start
the uncaring moon,
looking down on us.

00:00:26.694 --> 00:00:29.664 position:24% line:83% align:start
The lake that sank
into black abyss.

00:00:30.598 --> 00:00:32.199 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hey, tell me.

00:00:32.634 --> 00:00:35.537 position:19% line:83% align:start
Why did everyone I love
lie to me?

00:00:35.770 --> 00:00:36.971 position:38% line:89% align:start
They did.

00:00:37.104 --> 00:00:38.940 position:21% line:89% align:start
And I believed in it.

00:00:39.841 --> 00:00:42.877 position:13% line:83% align:start
But I only found one thing
outside of here.

00:00:43.443 --> 00:00:46.046 position:10% line:89% align:start
A world that's full of shit!

00:00:46.648 --> 00:00:47.682 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crackling]

00:02:20.675 --> 00:02:22.977 position:19% line:83% align:start
[TZVETA] The few years
after I left the orphanage

00:02:23.111 --> 00:02:24.112 position:33% line:89% align:start
weren't long,

00:02:24.244 --> 00:02:25.613 position:7% line:89% align:start
But they were more than enough.

00:02:25.747 --> 00:02:28.716 position:21% line:83% align:start
I witnessed how cold
the world could be.

00:02:30.118 --> 00:02:31.786 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
Please take a pamphlet.

00:02:32.252 --> 00:02:33.755 position:16% line:83% align:start
Do you have any children,
ma'am?

00:02:33.888 --> 00:02:35.222 position:19% line:89% align:start
Maybe they'd like one.

00:02:35.857 --> 00:02:38.760 position:35% line:83% align:start
Excuse me.
A moment of your time.

00:02:39.661 --> 00:02:40.895 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-[paper rustling]

00:02:42.897 --> 00:02:43.931 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crumbles]

00:02:46.067 --> 00:02:48.770 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:02:59.614 --> 00:03:01.082 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
Not enough.

00:03:01.516 --> 00:03:03.685 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'll have to find more work.

00:03:05.252 --> 00:03:06.486 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whimpering]

00:03:06.921 --> 00:03:08.388 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's cold.

00:03:08.723 --> 00:03:11.759 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:03:15.830 --> 00:03:16.864 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:03:21.169 --> 00:03:22.904 position:16% line:89% align:start
What's the matter, Pesha?

00:03:23.403 --> 00:03:25.338 position:19% line:89% align:start
Are you feeling hungry?

00:03:25.907 --> 00:03:26.941 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mm-mm.

00:03:27.942 --> 00:03:29.309 position:35% line:89% align:start
Of course.

00:03:29.443 --> 00:03:30.812 position:30% line:89% align:start
Sorry, sweetie.

00:03:31.445 --> 00:03:33.014 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'll fix something up.

00:03:33.581 --> 00:03:35.348 position:19% line:89% align:start
Give me just a minute.

00:03:39.954 --> 00:03:40.988 position:41% line:89% align:start
[chops]

00:03:41.989 --> 00:03:43.124 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
My Pesha...

00:03:43.256 --> 00:03:45.392 position:13% line:89% align:start
I won't let you go hungry.

00:03:45.927 --> 00:03:47.427 position:21% line:89% align:start
Please don't be sad.

00:03:47.695 --> 00:03:49.296 position:21% line:89% align:start
You're my only light,

00:03:49.429 --> 00:03:51.866 position:30% line:83% align:start
the last thing
the world hasn't taken.

00:03:51.999 --> 00:03:53.233 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:04:00.407 --> 00:04:01.408 position:21% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE EMPLOYEE 10A]
Hey, Letana?

00:04:01.542 --> 00:04:03.010 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-A moment, please.

00:04:03.343 --> 00:04:04.377 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:04.746 --> 00:04:06.480 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry to have to do this,

00:04:06.614 --> 00:04:09.382 position:27% line:83% align:start
but we'll have to
let you go after this month.

00:04:10.051 --> 00:04:11.919 position:10% line:89% align:start
You know, it is a recession.

00:04:12.053 --> 00:04:14.956 position:21% line:83% align:start
Every local business
has to make some cuts.

00:04:15.723 --> 00:04:16.758 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh.

00:04:18.593 --> 00:04:19.927 position:33% line:89% align:start
I understand.

00:04:20.061 --> 00:04:21.562 position:27% line:89% align:start
That's how it is.

00:04:22.196 --> 00:04:23.231 position:24% line:89% align:start
[door creaks shut]

00:04:24.031 --> 00:04:27.235 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'll have to find that new job
sooner than I expected.

00:04:27.367 --> 00:04:28.603 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:31.072 --> 00:04:32.807 position:41% line:83% align:start
Pesha.
Wake up.

00:04:33.074 --> 00:04:35.710 position:19% line:83% align:start
This isn't a good spot
to fall asleep.

00:04:35.843 --> 00:04:36.878 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:37.712 --> 00:04:38.980 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:04:40.748 --> 00:04:43.851 position:13% line:83% align:start
[LETANA] She drew a picture
of us smiling?

00:04:44.451 --> 00:04:46.687 position:16% line:89% align:start
And that looks like cake.

00:04:48.689 --> 00:04:52.492 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm not sure if she's ever
seen me smile like this.

00:04:54.327 --> 00:04:56.097 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm so sorry, Pesha.

00:04:56.230 --> 00:04:58.933 position:16% line:83% align:start
I wish I was able to buy
all the cake on Earth

00:04:59.066 --> 00:05:00.300 position:27% line:89% align:start
for you to enjoy.

00:05:01.301 --> 00:05:02.335 position:35% line:89% align:start
But maybe,

00:05:02.637 --> 00:05:04.739 position:27% line:83% align:start
I can still make
something happen.

00:05:05.006 --> 00:05:07.041 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:05:14.447 --> 00:05:15.616 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
We need food.

00:05:15.750 --> 00:05:17.552 position:19% line:89% align:start
I can't cut back more.

00:05:17.685 --> 00:05:19.821 position:7% line:89% align:start
I need to find a new job soon.

00:05:19.954 --> 00:05:20.922 position:35% line:89% align:start
Or else...

00:05:21.055 --> 00:05:21.956 position:35% line:89% align:start
[knocking]

00:05:22.089 --> 00:05:23.323 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:05:25.693 --> 00:05:27.061 position:24% line:89% align:start
Is there a problem?

00:05:27.195 --> 00:05:28.629 position:30% line:83% align:start
[LANDLADY 10A]
Don't you give me that, Letana!

00:05:28.763 --> 00:05:30.631 position:24% line:83% align:start
You know damn well
why I'm here.

00:05:30.765 --> 00:05:32.667 position:16% line:83% align:start
You're already six months
late on rent,

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:34.502 position:16% line:89% align:start
in case you've forgotten.

00:05:36.170 --> 00:05:37.572 position:33% line:89% align:start
I apologize.

00:05:37.705 --> 00:05:39.874 position:19% line:83% align:start
But I'm having a really
hard time finding work.

00:05:40.308 --> 00:05:42.610 position:16% line:83% align:start
[sighs] You think things
are only rough for you?

00:05:42.743 --> 00:05:45.613 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm no monster, so I hate
that you're making me say this,

00:05:45.746 --> 00:05:47.014 position:19% line:89% align:start
but if this continues,

00:05:47.148 --> 00:05:49.449 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'll have no choice
but to kick you out.

00:05:51.219 --> 00:05:52.452 position:33% line:89% align:start
I'm so sorry.

00:05:52.687 --> 00:05:54.922 position:21% line:83% align:start
Please, just give me
a week or two.

00:05:56.090 --> 00:05:57.692 position:30% line:89% align:start
[clock ticking]

00:06:07.335 --> 00:06:09.070 position:13% line:89% align:start
What's the matter, sweetie?

00:06:09.537 --> 00:06:11.072 position:19% line:89% align:start
You don't feel hungry?

00:06:13.908 --> 00:06:15.977 position:30% line:83% align:start
You need to eat
everything you can,

00:06:16.110 --> 00:06:18.212 position:21% line:83% align:start
or you won't grow up
big and strong.

00:06:18.346 --> 00:06:19.580 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:06:21.716 --> 00:06:24.652 position:30% line:83% align:start
Dear, come on.
This is important.

00:06:25.653 --> 00:06:27.655 position:24% line:89% align:start
Just eat, for mama.

00:06:28.022 --> 00:06:30.925 position:41% line:83% align:start
Please.
Be a good girl, Pesha.

00:06:32.727 --> 00:06:34.461 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[slams table]
-Listen to me, dammit!

00:06:34.595 --> 00:06:35.830 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:06:39.200 --> 00:06:41.168 position:16% line:89% align:start
Sweetie, I didn't mean...

00:06:41.302 --> 00:06:42.770 position:13% line:89% align:start
what I meant to say was...

00:06:43.470 --> 00:06:44.705 position:44% line:89% align:start
I...

00:06:45.339 --> 00:06:47.241 position:33% line:89% align:start
Mama, please.

00:06:47.642 --> 00:06:50.278 position:13% line:83% align:start
You haven't eaten anything
in so long.

00:06:50.578 --> 00:06:51.979 position:38% line:89% align:start
[sobbing]

00:06:52.113 --> 00:06:55.349 position:19% line:83% align:start
I swear I didn't wanna
make things worse for you.

00:06:55.750 --> 00:06:57.585 position:16% line:89% align:start
I wanted you to have it.

00:06:57.718 --> 00:06:59.153 position:33% line:89% align:start
Sorry, Mama.

00:07:00.087 --> 00:07:01.322 position:27% line:89% align:start
I didn't mean it.

00:07:01.454 --> 00:07:02.990 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[sobbing]
-[LETANA] Oh...

00:07:03.124 --> 00:07:04.592 position:33% line:89% align:start
I'm so sorry.

00:07:05.359 --> 00:07:06.560 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
I'm finished.

00:07:07.061 --> 00:07:09.363 position:19% line:83% align:start
I don't have any right
to call myself a mother

00:07:09.496 --> 00:07:11.132 position:19% line:89% align:start
to this perfect child.

00:07:12.499 --> 00:07:14.135 position:19% line:89% align:start
As long as I'm around,

00:07:14.434 --> 00:07:16.904 position:27% line:83% align:start
she'll never find
her own happiness.

00:07:18.639 --> 00:07:20.241 position:30% line:89% align:start
But what if...

00:07:20.374 --> 00:07:22.510 position:19% line:89% align:start
I suddenly disappeared?

00:07:22.777 --> 00:07:24.444 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:07:30.351 --> 00:07:31.552 position:24% line:89% align:start
If I weren't here,

00:07:31.686 --> 00:07:33.321 position:24% line:89% align:start
she could be happy.

00:07:33.453 --> 00:07:34.689 position:35% line:89% align:start
[splashing]

00:07:35.990 --> 00:07:36.891 position:38% line:89% align:start
Imagine.

00:07:37.024 --> 00:07:38.960 position:30% line:83% align:start
She could live
in the orphanage.

00:07:39.093 --> 00:07:41.629 position:27% line:83% align:start
The people there
could take better care of her.

00:07:42.096 --> 00:07:44.065 position:30% line:83% align:start
I wish I could
live there with her,

00:07:44.198 --> 00:07:48.102 position:19% line:83% align:start
to go back to the days
when the world still felt warm.

00:07:50.037 --> 00:07:52.707 position:21% line:83% align:start
I can't bear to live
in winter anymore.

00:07:52.840 --> 00:07:54.909 position:24% line:89% align:start
And it never ends.

00:07:56.476 --> 00:07:57.945 position:30% line:89% align:start
If this is it,

00:07:58.346 --> 00:07:59.780 position:13% line:89% align:start
I want to let her try cake,

00:07:59.914 --> 00:08:01.949 position:30% line:83% align:start
so she can have
one good thing.

00:08:03.417 --> 00:08:04.618 position:24% line:89% align:start
[doorbell ringing]

00:08:05.920 --> 00:08:08.189 position:10% line:83% align:start
[FEMALE BAKERY EMPLOYEE 10A]
Welcome, look around.

00:08:08.689 --> 00:08:11.125 position:27% line:83% align:start
What kind of cake
are you in the mood for?

00:08:11.993 --> 00:08:14.494 position:30% line:83% align:start
Oh, well, I...
You see um...

00:08:14.729 --> 00:08:17.765 position:13% line:83% align:start
I hoped I could get a cake
for my little girl.

00:08:18.966 --> 00:08:22.069 position:13% line:83% align:start
But no, I'll take a cookie.
That's all.

00:08:22.837 --> 00:08:26.474 position:35% line:83% align:start
Is that so?
I've got just the thing.

00:08:26.974 --> 00:08:29.343 position:33% line:83% align:start
Here you go,
I recommend this one.

00:08:29.477 --> 00:08:31.645 position:7% line:89% align:start
It's the most delicious I have.

00:08:31.946 --> 00:08:33.714 position:27% line:83% align:start
No! There's been
a misunderstanding,

00:08:33.848 --> 00:08:35.750 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm sure it's tasty,
but I can't afford something

00:08:35.883 --> 00:08:37.184 position:30% line:89% align:start
so extravagant.

00:08:37.752 --> 00:08:38.619 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:08:38.753 --> 00:08:39.754 position:33% line:89% align:start
On the house.

00:08:39.887 --> 00:08:41.922 position:16% line:83% align:start
-Please, it's all yours.
-Huh?

00:08:42.456 --> 00:08:43.824 position:24% line:89% align:start
All I ask in return

00:08:43.958 --> 00:08:45.793 position:19% line:83% align:start
is that the two of you
tell me if you like it.

00:08:45.926 --> 00:08:48.896 position:27% line:83% align:start
And make sure to
bring her with you next time.

00:08:49.030 --> 00:08:50.631 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:08:50.765 --> 00:08:52.099 position:33% line:89% align:start
I'll do that.

00:08:52.366 --> 00:08:53.667 position:35% line:89% align:start
I promise.

00:08:54.435 --> 00:08:55.369 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you.

00:08:55.504 --> 00:08:56.537 position:41% line:89% align:start
Truly.

00:08:56.670 --> 00:08:57.905 position:24% line:89% align:start
[doorbells tinkles]

00:08:58.172 --> 00:09:01.042 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:09:05.413 --> 00:09:06.747 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
Right.

00:09:07.448 --> 00:09:09.250 position:13% line:89% align:start
I can't give up so easily.

00:09:09.717 --> 00:09:11.185 position:21% line:89% align:start
She deserves better.

00:09:12.586 --> 00:09:13.854 position:16% line:89% align:start
I need to go back to her.

00:09:13.988 --> 00:09:16.190 position:10% line:89% align:start
And apologize for my yelling.

00:09:16.924 --> 00:09:19.960 position:7% line:83% align:start
I wouldn't hold it against her
if she hated me for that.

00:09:20.895 --> 00:09:22.630 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'll make it up to her.

00:09:24.498 --> 00:09:25.733 position:35% line:89% align:start
[giggling]

00:09:30.938 --> 00:09:32.606 position:24% line:89% align:start
[playful shouting]

00:09:33.407 --> 00:09:35.076 position:13% line:83% align:start
[LETANA] I'll tell her that
no matter what,

00:09:35.209 --> 00:09:38.112 position:30% line:83% align:start
the only thing
ever on my mind is her.

00:09:40.247 --> 00:09:43.284 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm realizing she doesn't know
how I feel.

00:09:43.818 --> 00:09:45.052 position:10% line:89% align:start
I've never been open with her

00:09:45.186 --> 00:09:47.088 position:21% line:83% align:start
about what's weighing
on my mind.

00:09:48.557 --> 00:09:49.790 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thuds]

00:09:51.992 --> 00:09:53.828 position:13% line:83% align:start
[MALE VAGRANT 10A] [scoffs]
No money to help me out,

00:09:53.961 --> 00:09:56.030 position:27% line:83% align:start
but the bitch can
afford to buy a cake?

00:09:57.064 --> 00:09:58.099 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thuds]

00:09:58.399 --> 00:09:59.633 position:35% line:89% align:start
[splashing]

00:10:02.670 --> 00:10:04.805 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:10:04.939 --> 00:10:06.541 position:38% line:83% align:start
[LETANA]
This cold world,

00:10:06.674 --> 00:10:10.111 position:7% line:83% align:start
it finally took the last thing
I have, away from me.

00:10:10.478 --> 00:10:12.146 position:27% line:89% align:start
But that's okay.

00:10:14.315 --> 00:10:17.318 position:21% line:83% align:start
Maybe now I can feel
warm in hell.

00:10:17.451 --> 00:10:19.720 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:10:23.657 --> 00:10:24.692 position:41% line:89% align:start
Pesha,

00:10:24.825 --> 00:10:26.760 position:19% line:89% align:start
I have one last dream.

00:10:26.894 --> 00:10:28.896 position:38% line:83% align:start
For you,
and children everywhere.

00:10:29.029 --> 00:10:31.765 position:24% line:83% align:start
May you never know
the extent of the pain

00:10:31.899 --> 00:10:33.602 position:16% line:89% align:start
this world can give you.

00:10:34.235 --> 00:10:36.103 position:10% line:89% align:start
Or if you can't be kept safe,

00:10:36.237 --> 00:10:39.273 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'd rather this world
simply cease to exist.

00:10:39.406 --> 00:10:41.308 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:10:41.442 --> 00:10:44.678 position:19% line:89% align:start
Ah, everything's cold.

00:10:44.812 --> 00:10:46.046 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ice crackles]

00:10:51.852 --> 00:10:53.320 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mama.

00:10:53.454 --> 00:10:54.488 position:35% line:89% align:start
Now, Pesha,

00:10:55.222 --> 00:10:57.526 position:19% line:83% align:start
you finally understand
why I'm here.

00:10:57.658 --> 00:10:59.860 position:27% line:83% align:start
To keep you safe
from this hell.

00:11:00.828 --> 00:11:02.329 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
Pepesha, get out!

00:11:03.030 --> 00:11:04.765 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SPIRIT]
Were those her memories?

00:11:04.899 --> 00:11:06.535 position:10% line:89% align:start
But if she drowned years ago,

00:11:06.667 --> 00:11:08.068 position:33% line:89% align:start
how is she...

00:11:08.202 --> 00:11:09.803 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KUFUFU] What'd you think,
you pain in the butt?

00:11:09.937 --> 00:11:11.872 position:21% line:83% align:start
As the curtains close
on this heart wrencher,

00:11:12.006 --> 00:11:13.741 position:21% line:89% align:start
not even I can laugh!

00:11:13.874 --> 00:11:15.776 position:16% line:89% align:start
But now, it's quiz time!

00:11:15.910 --> 00:11:17.111 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Here!
-Huh?

00:11:18.045 --> 00:11:19.747 position:30% line:83% align:start
Will our Heroes
be able to cheer

00:11:19.880 --> 00:11:22.249 position:38% line:83% align:start
Tzveta up
and make her smile again?

00:11:25.452 --> 00:11:27.656 position:44% line:83% align:start
Buzz!
Looks like your time's up!

